snippet.title: Road Fighter NES/Famicon TAS (4:49.76)
snippet.description:
This time is until the first completely black frame after level 4.
It's possible to play all levels again, but I think, that this game has no really end.

TASed it just, cause I was bored and cause I like this game. Maybe I'll TAS more Nes game in future.

Rerecords: 1303. Lol not much rerecords, but I didn't have to do that much in this TAS. Most rerecords were, cause I tried to always use the last possible frame to drive left/right.

Enjoy. ^^
